  "detailed_description": "Play the original Reversi game or play with the Othello starting positions in this highly-acclaimed strategy board game. The rules are simple, but the game is hard to master.<br><br>Reversi a strategy board game that involves two players, played on an 8×8 uncheckered board. Play against an AI player with 3 levels of difficulty (Easy, Medium, Hard).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/5c2617593b071a756b2eac98c4f5d3b8.poster.avif?t=1747214259\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/5c2617593b071a756b2eac98c4f5d3b8.webm?t=1747214259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/5c2617593b071a756b2eac98c4f5d3b8.mp4?t=1747214259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy the charms of LoFi music whilst you play in various temple-like locations.<br><br>Be able to create a giant board to play on, or maticuliously place pieces to roleplay matches or end games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/07846d09cafc88943b616ea088809f4f.poster.avif?t=1747214259\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/07846d09cafc88943b616ea088809f4f.webm?t=1747214259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/07846d09cafc88943b616ea088809f4f.mp4?t=1747214259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play 2 player local multiplayer with your friends or family. Rather than setting up a physical board, quickly play on your computer with Reversi Temple.",
  "about_the_game": "Play the original Reversi game or play with the Othello starting positions in this highly-acclaimed strategy board game. The rules are simple, but the game is hard to master.<br><br>Reversi a strategy board game that involves two players, played on an 8×8 uncheckered board. Play against an AI player with 3 levels of difficulty (Easy, Medium, Hard).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/5c2617593b071a756b2eac98c4f5d3b8.poster.avif?t=1747214259\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/5c2617593b071a756b2eac98c4f5d3b8.webm?t=1747214259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/5c2617593b071a756b2eac98c4f5d3b8.mp4?t=1747214259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy the charms of LoFi music whilst you play in various temple-like locations.<br><br>Be able to create a giant board to play on, or maticuliously place pieces to roleplay matches or end games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/07846d09cafc88943b616ea088809f4f.poster.avif?t=1747214259\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/07846d09cafc88943b616ea088809f4f.webm?t=1747214259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855830/extras/07846d09cafc88943b616ea088809f4f.mp4?t=1747214259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play 2 player local multiplayer with your friends or family. Rather than setting up a physical board, quickly play on your computer with Reversi Temple.",
